/******************************************************************
Stylesheet: 481px and Up Stylesheet

This stylesheet is loaded for larger devices. It's set to 
481px because at 480px it would load on a landscaped iPhone.
This isn't ideal because then you would be loading all those
extra styles on that same mobile connection. 

A word of warning. This size COULD be a larger mobile device,
so you still want to keep it pretty light and simply expand
upon your base.styl styles.

******************************************************************/

.header
	position relative
	margin 0 auto
	max-width max-width
	background transparent
.chosen-container,
.grid-item
	column(4)
.chosen-container
	overflow visible!important

#slider
	height 460px
	.rsContent
		.info
			width 100%
			height 460px
			margin 0 auto
			margin-top -460px
			position relative
			border 1px dotted grey
			max-width max-width
			overflow hidden
			.content
				text-align center
				position absolute
				width 50%
				height 40%
				border 1px dotted grey
				color grey
				hr
					height 0
					border-top 4px dotted blue
		img.big
			display block
		img.small
			display none
	.veckans
		.info .content
			top 30%
			left 5%

.single,
.archive
	#content
		padding-top 100px
	.media
		column(8)
		img
			width 100%
			height auto
	article
		column(4)
.home
	#push-spaces
		clear both
		.widget
			column(4)

